śBelinda 
01.01.1961 - 21.07.2015
Aged 54 years
In memory and honour of our dear colleague and friend Belinda Mason
Belinda was a Nurse Practitioner in the Urgent Care Centre
She dedicated 35 years to nursing at QMH. Sadly, Belinda lost her battle to cancer
She is remembered with much love and fondness from colleagues in the UCC and all who knew her X"Ů
